    "Header": "",
    "Description": "Through thoughtful upcycling, I've breathed new life into every piece of furniture and kitchen fixture, repairing, cleaning, and transforming them to showcase their beauty in fresh forms, colors, and fabrics. My commitment to reuse extends to every corner, ensuring that nothing goes to waste.",
    "Short Description": "Every aspect of our renovation has been meticulously crafted with the planet in mind. We've transformed our space with a focus on minimizing our environmental footprint.",
    "Details": "<p id=\"\">Before and after of the reception area. </p><p id=\"\">Repaired, changed color and fabric.</p><p id=\"\">Flooring has been changed to HDF.</p><p id=\"\">Curtain skirts changed to lighter color with a vintage effect.</p><p id=\"\">Lighting units were originally gold, changed to off white.</p><p id=\"\">The two wooden pieces on the wall aged 100+ years, were a part of an old castle in Upper Egypt. Got them from a collector. </p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\">Before and after of the Kitchen.</p><p id=\"\">Used the kitchen’s old wood, repaired it, changed its color, implemented a new design and added up more units. </p><p id=\"\">Re-used as much as I could and was environmentally conscious.</p><p id=\"\">The kitchen door was bought it from a collector, it’s an ancient door was a part of an old house in Egypt 80+ years ago. Up-lifted it to match the actual measurements, added more wood, colored and retouched it.</p><p id=\"\">‍</p>",
    "Image Gallery": "https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aeffb8dbd09f021218754_RNI-Films-IMG-626771D9-4D1F-4D23-8F03-A5D8C6783482.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/6616fc8cde4f08506a213cae_RNI-Films-IMG-282314E5-1C50-4E20-A789-B9994FBCBBED.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aeffb732c4c8b54ca5a7c_RNI-Films-IMG-C1565BD3-E56B-4EBA-9E13-3DFAC566A53A.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aeffaee4bd319348509dc_RNI-Films-IMG-81488246-55A6-4D55-8ED3-CB5DF3299FAA.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aeffa1e1c76198c96d233_RNI-Films-IMG-0CB56787-AEDD-4A39-87AC-84E558209365.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661af2960eb5ff09c29e2aea_RNI-Films-IMG-A9CF24FA-310C-4CF1-B9BB-7B14ED95E04D.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/6616ff449bcb61363c48f819_RNI-Films-IMG-5CCA998D-64A7-4887-B132-0A28ECBBADF1.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/6616ff448979511112628e2f_RNI-Films-IMG-9B7D99A4-EB94-4933-897C-375DA84BC037.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aed57661434c980854494_RNI-Films-IMG-CA336862-7569-4102-9BFF-BEB76F34501B.JPG; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aeffa8dbd09f0212186f5_RNI-Films-IMG-5A05EAF9-A527-4A07-BAE4-788443427B3B.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/6617017ebe3630b005ac47d9_RNI-Films-IMG-0BEDF48F-E107-4366-BAF8-02D798AAE12A.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/6617017d6a9cfa74768dcc6e_RNI-Films-IMG-F853A59A-93D5-4596-9E56-3578B3F02D58.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aedcf661434c98085ca3d_RNI-Films-IMG-B49432F1-298E-4E42-8F67-EBC42FA3EECD.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27f93f2dd6c8/661aeffb184f797879618a22_RNI-Films-IMG-16B68D40-7F94-4101-9938-5C747F90867B.jpg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6593930a237f27